                </ul>





            <h2>Research</h2>
                <p>Our research has shown that this header is clearer and more usable than the old NHS Choices header, and it expresses the NHS brand.</p>
                <p>Removing drop downs on larger screens, for example, has made it easier for people with motor skills problems or touchscreens.</p>
                <p>Get in touch to share your research findings if you've used this pattern.</p>







